[Basic]
Name=[8] Oil in the Center Bonus! v16.1 but something's twisted: CHAPTER 3
Briefing=-[Here we go again, welcome to Twisted Chapter 3!]-@@-HARDCORE!!-@I made Batle Fortresses have 200 HP, no more tryharding? Maybe..@-TROLLING-@I made Prism Tanks be able to attack air, to counter the allied buffs(like the following buff of the prism tower), Tesla Troopers now can attack air(and enter Battle Bunkers, and also GGIs can do that), and Patriots and Flaks now can attack ground!@-PRISM TOWERS OP!-@I made Prism Towers shoot very fast, with high damage, and able to attack air but now they cost 10,000 credits.@-BONUSES-@Apocalypse and Prism Tanks have a range of 15 now.@Battle Fortresses now have 10 slots in compensation for the debuff.@Tesla Troopers also got extended range for their AA properties to work.@That's what this chapter gets, I've got no more ideas, see ya on chapter 4@-Modified by shield_9
